      "name": "RMSE of hemolysis index predictions on calibration dataset",
      "description": "Root mean squared error (RMSE) of 0.0031 g/100 L was computed for NHI predictions relative to calibration measurements. This low RMSE is cited as evidence that simulation uncertainty is within acceptable bounds for regulatory submission. The metric is presented alongside R² and Pearson r to form the validation evidence package supporting the Accepted credibility decision. All three metrics are derived from the same in-sample calibration dataset.",
      "metricName": "Root mean squared error (RMSE)",
      "metricValue": 0.0031,
