      "note": "WEAKENER NOTE (inadequate-metrics): RMSE on calibration data does not assess whether the model correctly predicts relative hemolysis ranking across the 5 operating conditions in the COU. Deployment prediction error on the target pump geometry is the relevant metric; calibration RMSE is uninformative about this."
