    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required gradation levels for Model Risk Level 2. Validation evidence demonstrates R² = 0.94, Pearson r = 0.97, and RMSE = 0.0031 g/100 L against experimental hemolysis data, which the assessment team interprets as confirming model adequacy for identifying worst-case CPB operating conditions. Six factors are not assessed, consistent with MRL 2 scoping per ASME V&V 40 Table 1. The credibility assessment is accepted and the model is considered fit for the CPB COU decision.",
